'''Anthony M. Jones''' (born March 31, 1982), is a music producer/songwriter for EMI Music Publishing. He has produced for artists and groups such as [[R. Kelly]], [[Mary J. Blige]],<ref name="amj1">http://www.thisisrnb.com/2009/12/music-mary-j-blige-stay-bonus-track/</ref> [[Keri Hilson]],<ref name="amj2">http://repertoire.bmi.com/title.asp?blnWriter=True&blnPublisher=True&blnArtist=True&page=1&keyid=9869263&ShowNbr=0&ShowSeqNbr=0&querytype=WorkID</ref> and [[Neverest]].<ref name="amj3">http://www.bclocalnews.com/fraser_valley/abbynews/entertainment/116876013.html</ref>
The single "About Us" which he produced for [[Neverest]] <ref name="amj4">http://www.bestfan.com/blog/2011/01/bestfan-exclusive-interview-with-neverest/#more-18114</ref> recently won a SOCAN No. 1 Song Award.<ref name="amj7">http://www.socan.ca/jsp/en/pub/news_events/NeverestNo1.jsp</ref> The video reached #1 on the [[MuchMore]] video countdown.<ref name="amj5">http://www.muchmore.ca/music/muchmore-countdown-for-february-18-2011/</ref> This is his second successful single to be released in Canada. The first was "Last Time" by [[George Nozuka]]<ref name="amj6">http://artists.letssingit.com/george-nozuka-vxnlh/biography</ref>
